summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Tremouh Avenue from Kibourine Street to North Forty-fifth Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 17445, creating Local Improvement District No. 1643 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
